WASM C Bindings: C Bindings for Web Assembly
============================================
This repository is a collection of C bindigs for Web Assembly, it's ment
to compile any GLFW/OpenGL proyect to Web Assembly, with the minimum
of modification, and without depending on the compiler. 

See Live:
	https://pedroediaz.codeberg.page/proyects/triangle
	
Build:
		cd example
		bmake ARCH=WASM
	or:
		cd examlpe
		clang -DWASM --target=wasm32 -I/usr/include -nostdlib \ 
			-Wl,--no-entry,--export-all,--allow-undefined \
			main.c ../wasm.c -o main.wasm

Warning:
	* This proyect is incomplete, misses allmost all WebGL functions,
	and all the GLFW bindings.

